The paper deals with person re-identification using deep learning methods for visual recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves transfer learning and optimization processes, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The application areas mentioned in the abstract, such as video surveillance and autonomous driving, suggest that the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
